Version 1.4 released 2014-09-24

* Do 'git reset --hard' before doing 'git pull'.
This avoids machines getting stuck due to the cosmos repo being in an
unclean state and git refusing to update.

Version 1.3 released 2013-08-28

* Drop traces of unimplemented archival feature.

Version 1.2 released 2012-03-05

* Drop debian/ sub-directory.  Some cleanups for dpkg building.
Debian packaging split off to its own repository, see
<https://gitorious.org/cosmos/cosmos-dpkg>.

Version 1.1 released 2012-03-01

* No changes.

Version 1.0 released 2012-02-28

* Initial release.
